This test will check that shutdown works correctly from the Log out dialogue

<dl>
    <dt>Click Power button plugin on menu</dt>
        <dd>Logout dialogue appears</dd>
    <dt>Press Shut Down</dt>
        <dd>Machine shuts down</dd>
</dl>

This test will check that restart works correctly from the Log out dialogue

<dl>
    <dt>Click Power button plugin on menu</dt>
        <dd>Logout dialogue appears</dd>
    <dt>Press Restart</dt>
        <dd>Machine restarts</dd>
</dl>

This test will check that suspend works correctly from the Log out dialogue

<dl>
    <dt>Click Power button plugin on menu</dt>
        <dd>Logout dialogue appears</dd>
    <dt>Press Suspend</dt>
        <dd>Screen locks and machine suspends</dd>
    <dt>Restart the machine</dt>
        <dd>Machine comes out of suspend to an unlock dialogue</dd>
</dl>

This test will check that logout works correctly

<dl>
    <dt>Click Power button plugin on menu</dt>
        <dd>Logout dialogue appears</dd>
    <dt>Press Logout</dt>
        <dd>Machine logs out</dd>
    <dt>Login</dt>
        <dd>Machine logs back in</dd>
</dl>

